subtitleNullable: 26 years of data sales of drugs
descriptionNullable:
The dataset contains monthly sales of the drug R03 in the United States (in millions of US $) between 1992 and 2018.
R03 - Drugs for obstructive airway diseases

Sales data are resampled to the monthly periods. Data is already pre-processed, where processing included outlier detection and treatment and missing data imputation.
